there. I'm also going to leave a link in the
description box to a blog post about the process

00:03:35.629 --> 00:03:39.500
which will include some photos of how the
dye lasts across the weeks cos by the time

00:03:39.500 --> 00:03:42.720
you see this video i will have had it dyed
for a few weeks so you'l be able to see how

